35:51.358 --> 35:53.401
AMOS:
I am Pandasalt.

35:53.401 --> 35:55.403
And Regina and I
were together for a while,

35:55.403 --> 35:57.572
but if you think
I would ever hurt her...

36:00.367 --> 36:02.994
I didn't even know
she was dead until you told me.

36:04.788 --> 36:06.831
"My girlfriend drives me
crazy and sometimes

36:06.831 --> 36:08.083
I want to kill her."

36:08.083 --> 36:10.168
You posted that, right?

36:10.168 --> 36:14.005
Yes, but I-I wasn't...
being literal.

36:14.005 --> 36:16.716
Regina had problems;
she was a heroin addict.

36:16.716 --> 36:19.260
A fact her killer took full
advantage of ten months ago;

36:19.260 --> 36:21.137
made her death look like an OD.

36:21.137 --> 36:24.099
What, you think I'm the only one
who knew that she was on drugs?

36:24.099 --> 36:25.350
We think you're
the only person

36:25.350 --> 36:27.102
who ever talked
about killing her.

36:27.102 --> 36:29.771
Ten months ago,
I wasn't even in the country.

36:29.771 --> 36:32.315
I was, I was halfway through
a ten-week tour

36:32.315 --> 36:34.526
of South America.
HOLMES: We're aware.

36:34.526 --> 36:37.153
We have a picture of you
playing in Brazil

36:37.153 --> 36:38.738
the night that Regina died.

36:38.738 --> 36:41.157
So what are we even doing here?

36:41.157 --> 36:43.201
Did you forget
you perform in a mask?

36:43.201 --> 36:44.202
Could have been anyone
in those pictures.

36:46.496 --> 36:48.164
I have friends in Brazil.

36:48.164 --> 36:49.374
Reach out to them,
they'll tell you.

36:49.374 --> 36:50.542
I was hanging
out with them

36:50.542 --> 36:52.210
backstage that night
without the mask.

36:53.545 --> 36:55.338
They can probably
even send you pictures.

36:55.338 --> 36:57.549
Names and numbers.
No.

36:57.549 --> 36:59.634
No, first you tell me
where my daughter is.

36:59.634 --> 37:02.053
Why would we know
where your daughter is?

37:02.053 --> 37:03.805
Regina's daughter, whatever.

37:06.516 --> 37:08.643
A few months before
the Brazil show, I was in Lima.

37:08.643 --> 37:11.229
Regina called me,
said that she'd gotten clean

37:11.229 --> 37:12.647
and that she was pregnant.

37:12.647 --> 37:15.817
She said it was a girl
and that it was mine.

37:15.817 --> 37:17.944
The M.E. who performed
Regina's autopsy

37:17.944 --> 37:19.612
missed a few things;
maybe she missed that

37:19.612 --> 37:21.823
Regina was pregnant
when she died.

37:21.823 --> 37:23.074
No, you don't get it.
She'd already had the baby

37:23.074 --> 37:25.326
by then.
BELL: Back up a second.

37:25.326 --> 37:27.412
You said she called you in Lima,
told you she was pregnant...

37:27.412 --> 37:28.997
Yeah, she said
she didn't need anything,

37:28.997 --> 37:30.498
she just wanted me to know.

37:30.498 --> 37:31.916
She said she was
thinking of giving

37:31.916 --> 37:34.502
the baby to some
private adoption agency.

37:34.502 --> 37:36.713
That probably explains
where your daughter is now.

37:36.713 --> 37:38.882
Doesn't it?
No, no, 'cause I
talked her out of it.

37:38.882 --> 37:41.801
I told her I'd be there for her
and give her child support.

37:41.801 --> 37:43.803
Anything she wanted.
She said she'd think about it.

37:43.803 --> 37:45.263
Then,

37:45.263 --> 37:48.266
when I was in Brazil,
Regina called me again.

37:48.266 --> 37:49.893
She said she was
at the hospital.

37:49.893 --> 37:51.644
She'd just had the baby.

37:51.644 --> 37:53.480
She told me
she'd changed her mind.

37:53.480 --> 37:57.317
She told the adoption agency
she was going to keep it.

37:57.317 --> 38:00.153
She said she'd call me
if she ever needed anything.

38:02.155 --> 38:03.114
Give us a minute, would you?

38:11.956 --> 38:14.792
Assuming everything he says
is true, he was in Brazil

38:14.792 --> 38:17.212
the same day that Regina called
to say she'd had her baby.

38:17.212 --> 38:20.423
Based on our timeline,
that's the same day she died.

38:20.423 --> 38:22.801
That would mean she was killed
not long after she delivered.

38:22.801 --> 38:25.261
More specifically, it was
not long after she told

38:25.261 --> 38:27.055
the adoption agency she
was keeping the baby.

38:27.055 --> 38:28.973
We never had a motive
for Regina's death.

38:28.973 --> 38:30.808
Perhaps now we do.

38:30.808 --> 38:32.644
Whoever killed her
wanted her baby.

38:32.644 --> 38:35.021
So this wouldn't just be
a string of homicides.

38:35.021 --> 38:36.648
Could be a kidnapping, too.

38:43.655 --> 38:45.448
Wow.

38:45.448 --> 38:48.201
I don't even know
what to say to that.

38:48.201 --> 38:50.703
You think she
was lying to him?

38:50.703 --> 38:53.373
My guess is, she was
trying to get money out of him.

38:53.373 --> 38:56.501
The first time she called, she
said she didn't want anything.

38:56.501 --> 38:58.628
She'd already lined up
a private adoption.

38:58.628 --> 39:02.549
In my experience,
addicts make great con artists.

39:02.549 --> 39:04.968
Maybe she was
setting the table.

39:04.968 --> 39:06.761
The request for money
was going to come later.

39:06.761 --> 39:09.472
In your notes in the file
that you gave to my partner,

39:09.472 --> 39:11.599
you said you last saw
Regina in October.

39:11.599 --> 39:14.185
Her second phone call
to her ex-boyfriend,

39:14.185 --> 39:15.895
in which she told him
she'd just given birth,

39:15.895 --> 39:17.355
came in November.

39:17.355 --> 39:20.024
Exactly. You don't
think I would notice

39:20.024 --> 39:22.610
that she was
eight months pregnant?

39:22.610 --> 39:24.404
What?

39:24.404 --> 39:27.407
Regina's ex let us look
at his phone records.

39:27.407 --> 39:30.034
We were able to verify
that she did give him a call

39:30.034 --> 39:31.578
in the middle of November.

39:31.578 --> 39:32.870
When we looked for
the corresponding call

39:32.870 --> 39:33.955
in her records,

